a clear, concise, expository style and mastering the practical forms used in professional situations;
2. Oral presentation with emphasis on making informative 
and persuasive presentations with the effective use of technol-ogy and media;
3. Analytic thinking with emphasis on applying analysis, 
creative thinking, and the skills of systems thinking to the recognition, definition, and solution of personal, professional, organizational, and social problems;
